Package: camlrunm
Architecture: any
Section: devel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: runtime environment for running Caml Light bytecode
 Moscow ML is a light-weight implementation of Standard ML (SML),
 a strict functional language widely used in teaching and research.
 Version 2.01 implements the full SML language, including SML Modules,
 and much of the SML Basis Library.
 .
 http://www.dina.kvl.dk/~sestoft/mosml.html
 .
 This package contains the INRIA licensed camlrunm runtime for running
